title: Strangers

description.plain: Kenya Grace’s breakout hit “Strangers” explores the cyclical nature of romantic relationships and how they often follow a familiar pattern. The lyrics describe the experience of meeting someone new, falling into a routine, and eventually drifting apart, returning to the feeling of being strangers once again. The song reflects on the repetitive nature of these experiences and questions the authenticity of love in such a cycle.
